{"tid":14963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際】特朗普宣布將完全放棄生意，專注治理國家","createTime":"2016-11-30T17:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T18:23:54.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6846c416c17195a6a2dcb8545cab7759cc146e52","tid":14963,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"特朗普宣布將完全放棄生意　專注治理國家 (21:46)<br />\n2016/11/30<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0n8pc2tw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0n8pc2tw&h=234da087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n美國候任總統特朗普業務遍佈全球，引發利益衝突之虞。不過，這名億萬富商今日宣布，將完全放棄他的生意，專注於總統職務，但未有透露其企業日後如何營運。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在Twitter連續發布數則帖文，表示因要專注於治理國家，「讓美國再強大起來」，所以會完全捨棄他的生意。但他強調，他並非被迫放棄生意，而是因為國家事務明顯更重要。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普未有提及其集團會有何安排，但相信業務會交由子女接管。他指12月15日會偕同子女，在紐約召開記者會交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n據《華盛頓郵報》早前統計，特朗普的企業最少在18個國家有商業活動，遍及亞洲、南美和中東，而且生意類型多樣，包括地產、酒店、賭場和娛樂事業，令人擔心他上任後，會因私人利益轇轕而左右國家政策。<br />\n<br />\n現任總統奧巴馬和前總統喬治布殊的顧問律師，因應特朗普的潛在利益衝突，日前要求選舉人團不要任命他為下任總統。<br />\n<br />\n（獨立報）<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161130/s00005/1480513231330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161130%2Fs00005%2F1480513231330&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2e73cca8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161130%2Fs00005%2F1480513231330&h=b8ae771a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161130/s00005/1480513231330</a>"},{"pid":"744ba177950ea81ad068d69ac53a44f95203930f","tid":14963,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c8dccad600507015fb8e9e22663b522b9ec9c6","tid":14963,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3385e8130d95e3f68b611cc32e922e78b12291d6","tid":14963,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:00:23.000Z","msg":"燒山尋日先講完佢唔肯退落黎有利益衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d479a673c23202094ec764c785d65414c9ca26","tid":14963,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:07:48.000Z","msg":"哂氣，生意做到依個地步邊有得放棄，最多只係由明走去暗，換個傀儡董事，股份比哂屋企人"},{"pid":"1a5420ce980f75669e186bd6eac6baf234d63c57","tid":14963,"uid":26985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"有個仔架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}